headline: WEC Energy Gains From Demand Growth & New Investment
summary: WEC rides the rising C&I demand and a $28 billion clean-energy plan, but faces pressure from tough competition and regulations.

headline: State approves first large Wisconsin wind farm since 2011. Badger Hollow will power 30,000 homes
summary: Its 19 wind turbines will produce enough energy to power 30,000 homes, according to project developer Invenergy. The project will be ready by 2027.
